                            <comment id="12758800" author="pkamath" created="Wed, 23 Sep 2009 17:54:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In LOCast.getFieldSchema the following code needs to change:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
