&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if the ExpressionOperator returned from getExpression() has not calcuated its field schema (mFieldSchema) this can result in a NPE&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
